Chinaza Ịhụnanya Uchendu (amụrụ ya na 3 Disemba afọ 1997)  bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Naịjirịa onye n'agba bọọlụ  gaa n'ihu
O so n’otu ndị otu egwu bọọlụ nke ụmụ nwanyị Naịjirịa
Na ọkwa otu ọ na-egwuri egwu maka Rivers Angels tupu ọ kwaga Braga na Portugal
Uchendu na-egwuri egwu maka Rivers Angels nke njikọ ụmụ nwaanyi Naijiria site na mmalite nke afọ 2017 ruo na Jụlai afọ 2018 mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị site na enyemaka nke Braga na Portugal
N'oge 2018 Africa Women Cup of Nations Uchendu na-egwu egwuregwu ikpeazụ, ebe ọ nọrọ n'okpuru nkeji 8 tupu ngwụcha oge ahụ
O nyere otu n'ime penariti anọ n'asọmpi penariti nke butere otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụnwaanyị Naịjirịa
